# Docstrings
- follow flake8 rules from [setup.cfg](mdc:setup.cfg)
- Always docstring in the same line as '''.
- Use :func:, :class:,  :attr: for references
- Write shape of inputs and outputs when possible
- For dataclass, always document attributes as they are declared. Do not document in the class
docstring.

# Python
- Follow flake8 rules from [setup.cfg](mdc:setup.cfg)
- Use descriptive names for functions, classess and other members
- Use type hints for all function signatures
- Use logging functions from [logging.py](mdc:src/curobo/util/logging.py) for print and raising
warnigs, errors
- Avoid using deprecated functions
- Follow PEP 563 (Postponed Evaluation of Annotations)

# Writing Tests
- tests should be src/curobo/tests folder.
- Do not write unit tests for wp.kernel decorators.
- When writing gradient checking using gradcheck, use float32 and not float64.